title: Yoki senu Wedding Bell
original_name: 予期せぬウエディング・ベル
sinopse:
In the Yoki senu Wedding Bell series:

1. Saikai wa Kanbi na Tsumi (Snowed in with Her Ex)
2. Daifugou no Sanjuunichikan no Kyuukon (Thirty Days to Win His Wife)
3. Muku na Otome no Henshin (One Week with the Best Man)
4. Daifugou ni Kobamareta Hatsukoi (A White Wedding Christmas)
